products.name: CG2000 Golf Set - 10Clubs
products.description: The MacGregor Men's CG2000 Golf Set is ideal for golfers of all levels, featuring 10clubs in total complete with a MacGregor Stand Bag. The entry-level CG2000 package set offers unrivalled value with men’s options of steel or graphite shafts in the irons and also a stand or cart bag option. This package set features a Ti-Matrix Driver, Fairway wood, Hybrid, Stainless steel Irons from (6-SW), Putter and Golf Bag.
